  <compounddef id="TIME" kind="page">
    <compoundname>TIME</compoundname>
    <title>TIME$ Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">string-expression<sp/>=<sp/>TIME$(boolean-expression)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Returns the current time as a string in <bold>24-hour format</bold> (<computeroutput>HH:MM:SS</computeroutput>).</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>If <computeroutput>boolean-expression</computeroutput> is <computeroutput>TRUE</computeroutput>, the time is adjusted for the current time zone configured with <ref refid="SETTIMEZONE" kindref="compound">SETTIMEZONE Keyword</ref>, including daylight saving time (DST) if applicable.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>If <computeroutput>boolean-expression</computeroutput> is <computeroutput>FALSE</computeroutput>, or if no time zone has been set or loaded, the time is returned in <bold>UTC</bold> from the system clock.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect3 id="TIME_1autotoc_md584">
<title>Examples</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>TIME$(TRUE)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Might produce:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">14:37:05</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>TIME$(FALSE)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Might produce:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">13:37:05</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="TIME_1autotoc_md586">
<title>Notes</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Returned format is always fixed-width <computeroutput>HH:MM:SS</computeroutput>, with leading zeros where necessary.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Local time depends on whether a valid time zone has been configured via <ref refid="SETTIMEZONE" kindref="compound">SETTIMEZONE Keyword</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>DST adjustments are handled automatically when local time is requested.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For numeric access to components of the current time, see <ref refid="HOUR" kindref="compound">HOUR</ref>, <ref refid="MINUTE" kindref="compound">MINUTE</ref>, <ref refid="SECOND" kindref="compound">SECOND</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="HOUR" kindref="compound">HOUR</ref> 路 <ref refid="MINUTE" kindref="compound">MINUTE</ref> 路 <ref refid="SECOND" kindref="compound">SECOND</ref> 路 <ref refid="DAY" kindref="compound">DAY</ref> 路 <ref refid="YEAR" kindref="compound">YEAR</ref> </para>
</sect3>
